data.description: Absolutely stunning home of 3356 sf in ABM on 2.5 acres.  This neighborhood is secluded, quiet, spacious and serene. The deer are right at home as they move throughout the day. Kitchen has all new appliances Granite counters, and new gas water heater.  Plenty of space to enjoy in this lovely home.  You will love entertaining on the large back deck that has 3 french doors for access.   This home has a bonus room that can be a huge craft room or weight room that has luxury vinyl planks.  All appliances stay and some furniture is negotiable.  Zero turn mower is negotiable if not sold prior to closing.  Just imagine yourself in this luxurious home.
